owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS ComponentSetRule is a WINGS workflow class that represents a set of component rules in the workflow specification.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: ComponentSetRule

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS ComponentVariable is a WINGS workflow class that represents a component variable in the workflow specification.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: ComponentVariable

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS data variable is a WINGS workflow class that represents a workflow template artifact in OPMW and is a variable in the WINGS template specification.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: DataVariable

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS inout link is a WINGS workflow class that has an origin node, a destination node and a variable.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: InOutLink

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS input link is a WINGS workflow class that has a destination node and a variable.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: InputLink

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS Link is a WINGS workflow class that represents a link in the template specification.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Link

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS MetaData is a WINGS workflow class that represents the metadata pertaining to a template specification.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Metadata

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS Node is a WINGS workflow class that represents a node in the template specification. The node has components in templates.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Node

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS output link is a WINGS workflow class that has an origin node and a variable.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: OutputLink

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A parameter variable is a WINGS workflow class that represents a description of an input parameter of a workflow step.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: ParameterVariable
PortSetRule

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS workflow is a class in the WINGS Ontology that represents the entire workflow created in the WINGS workflow system.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Workflow

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS WorkflowInstance is a class in the WINGS Ontology that represents the workflow instance that is connected to a workflow execution file by the relation hasPlan workflowInstance.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: WorkflowInstance

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The WINGS workflow template is a class in the WINGS Ontology that represents the entire workflow template created in the WINGS workflow system.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: WorkflowTemplate
